Titolo: Rangi (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Rangi is a single-player virtual reality adventure puzzle game designed by Moroccan indie studio Funsoft and published by Digigo. It is currently available on Samsung Gear VR, and will be released on Oculus Rift later in 2017. It also has a Greenlight campaign on Steam. Rangi is distinguished by its tribal art and music, mythology and folklore, and African-inspired landscapes.
Several of the game developers are former members of Ubisoft Casablanca. The game was designed with Unity.